Disjoint-Set

Using union by rank and path compression:

Data structure that supports 3 operations

3 Functions:

MakeSet - is operation a 1 set with 1 item

union- take two sets and merge into 1 set

findSet - operation to return a identiy of a set which is usually an element in a set that acts as a represative of a set

Use:

Kruskal Algo

Find cylce in undirected set.

Two implementation
- union by rank and path compression

Node {
int rank
int data
Node Parent
}
